:VAR data subscribers

:GRAPH Customers
:TITLE Customers
:X-MAX 36
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR cumulative customers
:VAR data cum cust
:VAR Repeaters
:VAR data cum repeat cust

:GRAPH Revenue
:TITLE Revenue
:X-MAX 36
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR Reported Revenue[Interval]
:Y-MIN 0
:VAR data revenue[Interval]

:GRAPH Groupons
:TITLE Groupons
:X-MAX 36
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR Reported groupons sold[Qx3]
:VAR Reported groupons sold[Ann]
:VAR data groupons sold[Qx3]
:VAR data groupons sold[Ann]

:GRAPH Cost
:TITLE Cost
:X-MAX 36
:DOTS
:SCALE
:VAR Reported SGAM Cost[Interval]
:VAR "data SG&M cost"[Interval]
